### Going further for you and the environment

**Ecosphere** symbolizes our unwavering commitment to advancing environmentally responsible practices through eco-conscious product development and improvement.

Our overarching objective is to instigate transformative change, establish pioneering industry benchmarks, and lead our sustainable trajectory towards a more environmentally conscious future.

Ecosphere is an ongoing journey, we are continuously working on ways to reduce our environmental footprint and asking ourselves how we can do better; this starts with ethical formulations, sustainable packaging and material as well as responsible manufacturing.

We are committed to fulfilling Singapore Green Plan 2030.

![](https://freshening.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Vector-9-2-150x300.png)

### Towards Natural Formulations

Our range of products under the Ecosphere line are made from responsibly sourced ingredients. Our Research & Development team diligently endeavors to incorporate natural, plant-derived ingredients and biodegradable formulations into our work.

Our focus is on creating products that are not only powerful in performance, but also safe and gentle for you and the environment.

