### Towards Greener Packaging & Material

Containing 0% plastic and crafted from 100% compostable viscose material sourced from renewable wood derived from sustainably managed forests, our Ecosphere line of wipes embodies a dedication to ecological responsibility. With the capability to seamlessly revert to nature, these products complete the natural cycle. We proudly bear the mark of Forest Stewardship Council (FSC) certification, signifying our adherence to the highest standards of responsible forest management.

Our Ecosphere line uses packaging materials that minimise plastic consumption.

### Responsible Manufacturing

We consistently review our suppliers, and  only work with those who adhere to responsible sourcing practices and share an equal commitment to transparent and responsible business conduct. Additionally, within our manufacturing plants, we actively implement recycling and waste reduction measures.

We are proud to announce that our Singapore manufacturing plant will be solar-powered by the end of 2024, marking a significant stride towards sustainable and environmentally conscious operations.

